## Table Of Contents - [Table Of Contents](#table-of-contents) - [About](#about) - [Installation](#installation) - [Types](#types) - [Setups](#setups) - [KeyValue](#keyvalue) - [WideColumn](#widecolumn) - [Remote](#remote) - [Setting up the database server](#setting-up-the-database-server) - [Setting up the client](#setting-up-the-client) - [Links](#links) ## About Aoi.db is a collection of various database types to handle various types of data requirements! ## Installation

## Types

> - KeyValue - A simple database that stores key value pairs
>   - Usage: general purpose

> - WideColumn - A database that stores data in a column
>   - Usage: good for getting separate columns related to a primary column

> - Remote - A database that stores data in a remote server
>   - Usage: good for separating database extensive usage from main project/process
